file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3

info:
  title: openapiart go server generation
  description: A Sample Service in Go.
  version: 0.0.0

servers:
- url: https://{hostname}:{port}/{basePath}
  variables:
    hostname:
      default: 0.0.0.0
    port:
      default: "8080"
    basePath:
      default: api
